                  year in a row, Ducts Unlimited Mechanical Systems, Inc. received 
                  the prestigious Metal of Honor award from Hercules Industries. 
                  Rob Leishman, president, attributes the continued growth in 
                  sales for the company's ability to maintain the purchasing necessary 
                  to receive this award. Contratulations, Ducts Unlimited, for 
                  your continued success. </td>
