              <tr> 
                <td><strong>Westminster, CO - April 28, 2007</strong> - Ducts 
                  Unlimited Mechanical Systems Inc. was presented the Metal of 
                  Honor award from Hercules Industries at their annual awards 
                  dinner. Each year, Hercules Industries issues this award to 
                  its top customers. Ducts Unlimited President Rob Leishman says 
                  they spent over $500,000 last year with this vendor and this 
                  is the third year in a row to receive the award. He also compliments 
                  Hercules for acknowledging their best customers in such a public 
                  fashion.</td>
