                  presented Ducts Unlimited Mechanical Systems with their Customer 
                  Loyalty Award. Although not used exclusively, Carrier is certainly 
                  one of our leading providers of heating and AC units says Rob 
                  Leishman, President of Ducts Unlimited. The award will be displayed 
                  proudly in the lobby of the company headquarters. </td>
